Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:11.28,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur0.3\move(2500,810,1772,810,0,500)\t(3500,4000,\4a&HFF&)}A Wandering Chimera
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Just why doesn't she lose her weight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Doesn't one usually lose it after giving birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought as well, but now that's over and her weight hasn't gone down at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even giving her less to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she isn't feeling well after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks fine, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let her keep her fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It increases her attack stats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're part of the reason her staying fat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep feeding her those cat snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Evening, Satone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you sit down over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Around when you said, "I'm going to protect Rikka even if it costs my life!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, how about a fight to refresh our memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at Togashis' dining table.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a demilitarized zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You were one step away from death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not any closer than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She took control over Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you betraying me, my servant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems pretty attached to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you always been this close?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, lately she comes around every day to play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Chimera...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any complaints about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering where she kept going out sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was to your place, Shichimiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She comes every day and keeps begging for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a troublesome fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Food?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You feed her as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She keeps purring until I give in and give her some in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Chimera's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really not easy being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Touka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you arrive here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Around when you said, "I'm willing to die for Rikka's sake."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come in using the veranda as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the front entrance of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not telling you how I opened the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please refrain from just entering someone else's home in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner gave me her permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I lent her our spare key so she can see how things are going at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she'll be worrying about Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect for Kuzuha to change sides to the enemy as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the "enemy" here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen, Chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not working at that Japanese restaurant anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So stop dropping by to get food from the head chef every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if you did or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying Chimera comes to your place as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:03:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she comes to the restaurant I used to work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like she makes the head chef there feed her every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the reason why Chimera can't lose weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,600,0,,It's just because she's a huge glutton!
